(window.webpackJsonp=window.webpackJsonp||[]).push([[189],{816:function(n,e){n.exports="\x3c!-- \ntitle: Docker\nsort: \n--\x3e \n# Docker入门\n\n## 基础命令操作\n\n- 基础信息\n\n  `docker version`\n\n- 镜像加速配置文件\n\n  `vi /e/d/daemon.json`\n\n### 启动第一个容器\n\n`docker run -d -p 80:80 nginx`\n\n> run \t创建并运行一个容器\n>\n> -d\t后台运行\n>\n> -p\t端口映射\n>\n> nginx\t镜像名称\n\n- 查看正在运行的容器\n\n  `docker ps -a 所有容器`\n\n- 停止\n\n  `docker stop / kill`\n\n### 镜像操作\n\n```bash\ndocker image ls\t\t# list all docker image\ndocker ps --all\t\t# all container\n\n# Build own image\ndocker build --tag bulletinboard:1.0 .\ndocker run --publish 8000:8080 --detach --name bb bulletinboard:1.0\ndocker build --tag bulletinboard:1.0 .\n\n# Share to dockerhub\ndocker tag bulletinboard:1.0 <Your Docker ID>/bulletinboard:1.0\nocker push <Your Docker ID>/bulletinboard:1.0\n```\n\n- 详细信息\n\n  `docker image inspect name`\n\n- 搜索\n\n  `docker search name`\n\n- 获取\n\n  `docker pull name`\n\n- 列表\n\n  `docker image list`\n\n- 导出\n\n  `docker image save nginx > docker-nginx.tar.gz`\n\n- 导入\n\n  `docker load -i name`\n\n- 删除\n\n  `docker rm nginx:latest`\n\n  删除全部\n  `docker rm -f 'docker ps -a -q' `\n  \n- 彻底清除\n\n  `docker system prune -a -f`\n\n## 配置修改\n\n`/var/lib/docker/containers/xx/config.v2.json`\n\n### 换源\n\n`Setting->Docker Engine->\"registry-mirrors\"`\n\n## 常用镜像\n\n### DVMA\n\n```bash\ndocker pull vulnerables/web-dvwa\ndocker run -d -p 80:80 vulnerables/web-dvwa\n# admin password\n```\n\n## Code-Server"}}]);